quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  78,1,"What are they asking (one another) about?"
  78,2,"About the great news, (i.e. Islâmic Monotheism, the Qur’ân, which Prophet Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم brought and the Day of Resurrection)"
  78,3,"About which they are in disagreement."
  78,4,"Nay, they will come to know!"
  78,5,"Nay, again, they will come to know!"
  78,6,"Have We not made the earth as a bed,"
  78,7,"And the mountains as pegs?"
  78,8,"And We have created you in pairs (male and female, tall and short, good and bad, etc.)."
  78,9,"And We have made your sleep as a thing for rest."
  78,10,"And We have made the night as a covering (through its darkness),"